---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Bathroom Remodeling"
  description={`Bathroom remodeling in Asheville & Hendersonville, NC: showers, tile, fixtures and more from licensed remodel plumbers. Call ${site.phone} today.`}
  heroTitle="Create a Bathroom That Feels Like a Spa"
  heroSubtitle="Get started on your bathroom remodel in Asheville or Hendersonville, NC today."
  heroImage="/images/gallery/gallery-02.jpg"
  listHeading="3 ways to elevate the look of your bathroom"
  listItems={[
    'Fill your bathroom with beautiful tile flooring.',
    'Add a brand-new shower for a sleek, modern look.',
    'Give your bathroom fancy upgrades with new fixtures and features.',
  ]}
  listNote="Don't make your bathroom remodel a DIY project. Count on the expert bathroom remodel plumbers at Nesbitt's Plumbing."
  ctaHeading="Dreaming of a Spa-Like Bathroom?"
>
  <p>
    Imagine stepping into your bathroom and feeling like you're entering a luxurious resort spa.
    You immediately feel more relaxed and at peace as your worries melt away. If you have a
    vision of the perfect bathroom, Nesbitt's Plumbing can turn it into reality. We specialize in
    bathroom remodels in Asheville &amp; Hendersonville, NC.
  </p>
  <p>
    We handle everything from updating your shower to installing a new toilet. Your bathroom
    doesn't have to be boring. Call us now at
    <a href={site.phoneHref} class="font-semibold text-drop-600 hover:underline">{site.phone}</a>
    to schedule your bathroom remodel in Asheville or Hendersonville, NC today.
  </p>
</ServiceLayout>
